---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../styles/base.css";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> August 2, 2025</p>
      <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> August 2, 2025</p>

      <p>Tech for Palestine (“we,” “our,” or “us”) is a registered 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization committed to the principles of transparency, respect, and digital dignity. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our website, <strong>techforpalestine.org</strong>.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Information You Provide Directly:</strong> name, email, etc.</li>
        <li><strong>Technical Information:</strong> browser, device, general location. We avoid invasive tracking.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To respond to inquiries</li>
        <li>To support programs and outreach</li>
        <li>To improve the website</li>
        <li>To meet legal obligations</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell or trade your information.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">3. Sharing of Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Only with necessary service providers</li>
        <li>When legally required</li>
        <li>To protect rights or safety</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">4. Your Choices and Rights</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Opt out of email updates</li>
        <li>Request access, correction, or deletion of data</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Email us: <a href="mailto:contact@techforpalestine.org" class="text-green-700 hover:text-green-800">contact@techforpalestine.org</a></p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">5–9. Other Info</h2>
      <p>We protect data, avoid collecting info from children, and may link to external sites. This policy may change over time.</p>
  </main>
</Layout>
